com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services

Class OrderDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services.OrderDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Named(value="search_order")
 @ViewScoped
public class OrderDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class OrderDetails is a service class that being used to search and present the details of the order and to cancel it. When using the class we can set the order id and than the onload gets the order object. Once we loaded the the order we can get the order object. In addition, we can use the search method which is being used in the "View / Cancel Order" page - view-order.xhtml.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gil Danielly
